instructions: Put the charger in the middle of the tablecloth
Put the dinner fork to the left of the charger
The the dinner knife to the right of the charger
Put the salad fork on the left side fo the dinner fork
Put the salad knife on the right side of the dinner knife
Put the soup spoon on the right of the salad knife
Put the Dessert spoon above the charger with its head facing towards the forks
Put the Dessert Fork below the Dessert Spoon and between the charge with the tines facing the knives
Put the bread plate above the forks
Put the butter knife on the bread plate orientated Northwest
Put the water glass above the salad knife
Put the napkin on the plate
